description:
On today's Dan Patrick Show. DP discusses the Kyler Murray situation. Are his days in Arizona numbered? And former Sunday Night Football Sideline Reporter Michele Tafoya joins us to discuss what it was like being on the call for her last game , and the emotions that came with it.
